title: The Client
description: In this Dateline classic, Andrea Canning reports on a realtor from Little Rock, Arkansas who goes missing after showing a house. The search leads detectives on a gripping chase. Will she be found before it's too late? Originally aired on NBC on April 17, 2016
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
